An item can be flagged as Socked or not, can be part of a production process and/or can be a bill of materials. Item type is the only one for which a cost type calculation can be configured. Service type can be used to configure consultancy, transport or insurance services. Service type can be purchased or sold but can not be stocked. A service can be a bill of materials.
